item.title: CVE-2023-6139|2024-08-02T08:21:17.246Z -- unknown -- essential%20real%20estate
item.description: The Essential Real Estate WordPress plugin before 4.4.0 does not apply proper capability checks on its AJAX actions, which among other things, allow attackers with a subscriber account to conduct Denial of Service attacks.

item.title: CVE-2023-6140|2024-08-02T08:21:17.679Z -- unknown -- essential%20real%20estate
item.description: The Essential Real Estate WordPress plugin before 4.4.0 does not prevent users with limited privileges on the site, like subscribers, from momentarily uploading malicious PHP files disguised as ZIP archives, which may lead to remote code execution.

item.title: CVE-2023-6141|2024-08-02T08:21:17.717Z -- unknown -- essential%20real%20estate
item.description: The Essential Real Estate WordPress plugin before 4.4.0 does not apply proper capability checks on its AJAX actions, which among other things, allow attackers with a subscriber account to conduct Stored XSS attacks.
